Omg, thank you so much! I've been looking for these forever. I was so sad when the TV show got cancelled :(
I'll seed this indefinitely.

Yeah. Believe it or not I never watched the show when it first came out and just finished watching the whole thing last week. I had to know what happened next!

Stuff like this makes you realize what utter morons the TV Execs are sometimes. Totally mindless programming can go on for 9 or 10 seasons while quality programming gets axed.

(Guess we get what we pay for)

I previously upped this on Demonoid and it only lasted a day and 30 0r 40 downloads before it got axed.
Yeah, thanks again for the up. Also, idk if you've ever watched the show Kings, but it's also another prime example of quality programming getting the axe way before its time.
Thank you SO much dude! Really appreciate the share! :)
